primary.context: Customer wants to settle their maintenance fee balance
primary.detail: Agent successfully verified the caller and sent a payment link via text and email.

steps: Caller requested to pay maintenance fees.
Agent performed account lookup via caller ID.
Agent requested name verification; caller provided a different name than the spelling provided later.
Agent confirmed contact information on file.
Agent triggered payment link delivery via text and email.

clarifications.note: Initial name provided did not match record

actions.detail: Sent link to cccirone@msn.com and phone on file

insights.summary: The customer successfully requested and received a maintenance fee payment link after a brief name verification step.
